trans-unit.source: Provides an accessor to the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um acessador para a classe <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> method is called from an <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode> object, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object is initially positioned on the node from which the method was called.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> método é chamado de um <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode> objeto, o <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> objeto é inicialmente posicionado no nó do qual o método foi chamado.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> method is called from an <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument> object or an <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> object, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object is positioned on the root of the document.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> método é chamado de um <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument> objeto ou um <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> objeto, o <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> o objeto é posicionado na raiz do documento.

trans-unit.source: For examples of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> method, see the <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument>, or <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> classes.
trans-unit.target: Para obter exemplos do <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable.CreateNavigator%2A> método, consulte o <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument>, ou <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> classes.
